OL,7,FDion's rare condition causes
OL,8,Fprogressive muscular inflexibility.
OL,10,FHer struggles are documented in her
OL,11,F2024 documentary I Am: Celine Dion, in
OL,12,Fwhich she spoke about her desire to
OL,13,Freturn to performing.
OL,15,FIn June, at the premiere of the
OL,16,Fdocumentary, she said that returning
OL,17,Frequired therapy, "physically,
OL,18,Fmentally, emotionally, vocally".
